### 1. Place Order from Checkout
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/checkouts/{{checkoutId}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{requestId}}

{
  "customerNotes": "Please handle with care."
}

> {% client.global.set("orderId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 2. Get Order Detail
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. List My Orders (Authorized)
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/me/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
